---
id: P-DP-02
title: 헬스체크 패턴
stage: Deploy
layer: Infra
pattern_family: Release
tech_tags: [liveness probe, readiness probe, graceful shutdown, Kubernetes]
linked_errors: [E-DP-03, E-DP-04]
linked_flows: [F-DP-02]
