id: P-QP-04
title: 커넥션 풀 튜닝 패턴
stage: Design
layer: Infra
pattern_family: Persistence
tech_tags: [커넥션 풀, PgBouncer, 서버리스, Prisma]
linked_errors: [E-QP-07, E-QP-08]
linked_flows: [F-QP-04]
linked_prompts: [PR-QP-04]
