---
id: E-RT-10
title: 메모리 누수
error_class: Runtime
symptoms:
  - 메모리 사용량 증가
  - 애플리케이션 느려짐
  - OOM 에러
exact_messages:
  - "FATAL ERROR: CALL_AND_RETRY_LAST Allocation failed"
  - "JavaScript heap out of memory"
  - "Cannot allocate memory"
tech_tags:
  - Memory Management
  - Garbage Collection
  - Profiling
  - Performance
linked_patterns: []
