---
id: E-ST-01
title: Props 타입 불일치
error_class: Syntax-Type
symptoms:
  - TypeScript 컴파일 에러
  - 런타임에 예상 값이 없음
  - 컴포넌트가 예상대로 작동하지 않음
exact_messages:
  - "Type 'string' is not assignable to type 'number'"
  - "Property 'onClick' does not exist on type"
  - "Expected 1 argument, but got 2"
tech_tags:
  - React
  - TypeScript
  - Props
  - Type Safety
linked_patterns: []
