---
id: E-ST-08
title: 제네릭 제약 조건 오류
error_class: Syntax-Type
symptoms:
  - 제네릭 타입 인수 오류
  - 제약 조건 위반
  - 타입 추론 실패
exact_messages:
  - "Type 'string' does not satisfy the constraint 'number'"
  - "Type 'MyClass' does not satisfy the constraint 'extends { id: number }'"
  - "Generic type 'T' could not be inferred from usage"
tech_tags:
  - TypeScript
  - Generics
  - Type Constraints
  - Type Safety
linked_patterns: []
